      "content": "i get that, but my doctor just seems so stuck on the pills. i've been reading a lot online about how some people use high doses of vitamin K and garlic to naturally regulate things so they don't need the meds anymore. if i just really ramped up the spinach and the garlic every day, wouldn't that eventually stabilize me? it seems like a much more natural way to go than a chemical pill.",
